       <p>
	 The <title key="HOURS_VIRGIN" type="alternate">Little Office of the Blessed Virgin</title>, or <title key="HOURS_VIRGIN">Hours of the Virgin</title>, is a popular cycle of prayers, hymns, and other readings to be performed at various times throughout the day in devotion to the <persName key="Mary">Virgin Mary</persName>.
    </p>
    <p>
      The cycle is divided into eight canonical hours, each with their own set of psalms, hymns, prayers and other readings.
    </p>
